      datastructures.BST_Map<K,V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Map<K,V>
public class BST_Map<K extends java.lang.Comparable<? super K>,V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>

A table satisfying interface Map with key-value pairs satisfying interface Map.Entry and Comparable. The method compareTo compare the keys in the elements. Two element for which method compareTo gives 0 are not allowed. The elements are contained in a BinarySearchTree with no balancing.

Version:
(2005)
Author:
(Bror Bjerner)
